						</span>
                    </div>
					<a class="btn" onclick="nextpage(this)" href="#">Next</a>
				</div>
				
				
			
			</form>
		</div>
		<div class="col-lg-8" id="box_for_the_form">
			<div id="tv1">
				<pre >
                    <span class="name_of_the_person">____ (NAME)
                    ____</span>

                    <span class="date_of_application">____ (DATE)</span>

                    <span class="email_of_emp">____ (EMAIL)</span>

                    To <span class="company_name">_____(COMPANY),</span>
                    I am formally requesting you to give me few days leave of absence. I have finished almost all the projects assigned to me with only one remaining which I have given to my assistant to take care of it since he is as experienced just as I am in handling that remaining project. 

                    Thank you for your consideration. 

                    Yours Sincerely, 
                    <span class="name_of_the_person">______(NAME)</span>
